  "lines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 1,
      "text": "Russia is well aware of this fact and has capi[unclear]ized upon this fact.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "text": "They have in this way been able to penetrate our Radar System undetected.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "To conclude:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "The present situation can be blamed upon the various governmental",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "agencies who in the past have scoffed at and ridiculed people who",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "have reported these sightings.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "Now we are about to pay with 60,000,000 American lives or more.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "\"Some price\".",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "Our one hope is that Russia and China will go to war against one another.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "This then will give us time to created an effective and efficient Radar",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "system that cannot be penetrated.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "I am not a Prophet of Doom, just an American Citizen who is concerned",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "about the future of America.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "Sincerely yours,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
